%C A185787 * Every multisection of every row, every column, and every diagonal is linearly recurrent with signature (3,-3, 1). Indeed, every "linear staircase sequence", T(n+h*u,k+h*v), for fixed n,k,u,v, with h=0..oo, is linearly recurrent with signature (3,-3,1).
%C A185787 Let F(n) be the set of the first n numbers in row n together with the first n numbers in column n, so that F(1) = {1}, F(2) = {2,3,5}, F(3) = {4,6,8,9,13}, etc. Then n is in F(A051125(n)).
